    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who pass along or reveal information originating in another source or from another person or deity. An example is in religion, where a human may be said to have transmitted a message from a divine source.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
